:09.000Z","msg":"又唱k"},{"pid":"342e15de080a21cae76d0b7c1a3319c77c29991f","tid":1203014,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:18:31.000Z","msg":"有人用棍拍野deam beat 既時候唔好劣<br />\n一齊叫同一句口號加士氣避免士氣此消彼長<br />\n有心理學背後原理<br />\n對陣口號可參考港隊打氣口號<br />\n拍拍~拍拍拍~DIE FOR HONG KONG<br />\n<br />\n引用 雞肉大師 巴打:<br />\n要佢哋一齊嘶哮， 進入同一個呼吸節奏 同一個心跳步伐 <br />\n配合戰鼓(你搵個大水樽好撚大嗰啲 求其搵嘢敲佢有節奏嘅)打拍子 就會將一堆散兵游勇聚合成一個群體<br />\n以往慣例邊個大聲公喇叭就死邊個， 二來呢啲設備貴<br />\n但係水樽就可以有好多個 水樽買得起<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外大家小心雙眼，戴眼罩被人噴油漆就喪失視力，唔戴又會比人插眼<br />\n<br />\n大家亦小心近距離突然由下巴向上大力推有機會導致頸椎受傷 請各位注意安全免生危險"},{"pid":"4693497eca6a20ad9306654a94235d1031ded262","tid":1203014,"uid":171192,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bcc0dd8e18d22c9cb1ce88577f3959362b88ca49","tid":1203014,"uid":39575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:18:09.000Z","msg":"又唱k"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:19:14.000Z","msg":"小心販民班仆街控場！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前日聲稱預演點知叫人散水<br />\n尋日聲稱好嬲又無有效狙擊條例嘅行動<br />\n消耗民間士氣高手<br />\n推到販民仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99f746644b6058e93967b3f17084475e3c5d2ea1","tid":1203014,"uid":39575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4693497eca6a20ad9306654a94235d1031ded262","tid":1203014,"uid":171192,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bcc0dd8e18d22c9cb1ce88577f3959362b88ca49","tid":1203014,"uid":39575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:18:09.000Z","msg":"又唱k"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:19:14.000Z","msg":"小心販民班仆街控場！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前日聲稱預演點知叫人散水<br />\n尋日聲稱好嬲又無有效狙擊條例嘅行動<br />\n消耗民間士氣高手<br />\n推到販民仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:20:38.000Z","msg":"佢10點 我地5點霸撚左個頭位先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51d3ffe9e6b54b3fae33ff8795ec8ff3b81ff5a5","tid":1203014,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8a5f1c71cbdb46ebe505104f06a5251e0d9d8e12","tid":1203014,"uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:14:34.000Z","msg":"大家聽日一定要出嚟呀,  事態緊急呀."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:21:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/OhVPE09.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOhVPE09.png&h=a8323b03&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d9b42408a10e3d4bbd31c0ac71bc308ba52f117c","tid":1203014,"uid":226955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:21:16.000Z","msg":"香港人仲有機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家一齊撐到政府撤回逃倒為止！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />各位原諒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港宜家正值歷史危機當前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我有少少嘢想同大家講</span><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>唔想勇武咪和理非囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唱聖詩又好，想成隊百人管弦樂團一齊奏交響曲都得呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支持市民大眾繼續不斷以合法方式反送中</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一百萬人遊行只係個開始，大家仲有好多好多嘢可以做，例如今晚開始直到12號喺政總舉行嘅祈禱聖詩會，周街燈柱貼宣傳反送中單張，罷工罷課等，我希望大家要明白一樣嘢，任何願意作出反惡法嘅行動都應該要支持！香港人唔可以再比三毛分化，和理非同勇武必須一齊合作，佔大多數嘅和理非請用盡一切合法方法反對逃犯條例，逃犯條例絕對唔可以通過，否則我地同下一代就會生長喺講句說話都要就住就住，擔驚受怕嘅環境之中，大家絕對唔可以比逃犯條例過到<br />\n<br />\n我地應該要接受香港和理非佔大多數呢個事實，大多數人都唔會衝始終法律後果太重，所以大家可以用合法方式全力阻止惡法，只要係合法渠道去反送中，我相信唔少人都唔介意做多兩步，有啲人可能覺得有啲和理非行動聽起上嚟好似好膠，但請唔好理人點做，只要記住大家都係反送中嘅同路人，我地就應該尊重同埋支持佢地，支持和理非不斷以各種合法途徑反送中。去爭取更多市民同國際社會反送中。唔好話無用，你去做起碼仲有1%會成功，完全唔做就絕對唔會成功。大家一定要盡自己可以承受到嘅所有後果同力量，以政府徹回逃犯條例為成功目標。請記住，唔好再鬧分化，和理非有和理非做，其他人有其他人做，兄弟爬山，各自努力。<br />\n<br />\n歷史例子：<br />\n柏林圍牆冧之前幾個月冇人會覺得有生之年可以見到冧牆嘅一日，03年23條同12年國教都冇人會覺得可以令政府撤回23條同國教，正如今次亦都冇人會覺得可以令政府撤回逃犯條例。<span style=\"color: red;\">再強調一次，唔好話無用，你去做起碼仲有1%會成功，完全唔做就絕對唔會成功。</span>"},{"pid":"73d50f949ccd18c71cb22b998892bbd76ae096db","tid":1203014,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T15:03:55.000Z","msg":"聽日11點先開大會<br />\n<br />\n6項口頭質詢之後就係 送中二讀<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr18-19/chinese/counmtg/agenda/cm20190612.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr18-19%2Fchinese%2Fcounmtg%2Fagenda%2Fcm20190612.htm&d=%2FodnS2mEGvHoUZPzyf%2FmNRmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=36136a36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr18-19/chinese/counmtg/agenda/cm20190612.htm</a>"},{"pid":"4de9e8086f1447bf37fd6fd24efb483997af1ace","tid":1203014,"uid":4064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T15:04:45.000Z","msg":"［長期頂置］612野餐前捉Pokemon指南<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1203672/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1203672/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n有巴打好有心做左地圖<br />\n如果各位唔知去邊又去唔到金鐘就去捉下精靈啦！<br />\n<br />\n有人擺緊現場圖<br />\n集中討論"},{"pid":"ad574beac2f3b9016c54a610787d079dbfa00dac","tid":1203014,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T15:06:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 鄺仔同示威者夾住Ｄ<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />警<br />\n揸完身份證要道謙先比走<br />\n有個女士講「學堂唔識教，我地教佢地做人要有禮貌」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />道謙之後Ｄ<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />警笑笑口咁行開"},{"pid":"b22f431110047498ed230d200e7f8355988723b1","tid":1203014,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T00:18:11.000Z","msg":"推"}]}